WEBVTT

00:03:59.800 --> 00:04:01.160
and what was not.

00:04:03.320 --> 00:04:06.616
What's worse is that
we let these false ideologies

00:04:06.640 --> 00:04:09.376
invade our perception of ourselves,

00:04:09.400 --> 00:04:12.736
and they still continue
to infect our cultural identity

00:04:12.760 --> 00:04:15.200
as African-American women today.

00:04:16.720 --> 00:04:18.216
So what did we do?

00:04:18.240 --> 00:04:22.256
We went to the hair salon
every six to eight weeks,

00:04:22.280 --> 00:04:23.656
without fail,

00:04:23.680 --> 00:04:27.016
to subject our scalps
to harsh straightening chemicals

00:04:27.040 --> 00:04:28.976
beginning at a very young age --

00:04:29.000 --> 00:04:31.056
sometimes eight, 10 --